────────────────────────────────────────────
          FIELD TRANSMISSION [001]
────────────────────────────────────────────
             ODE TO JULIA
────────────────────────────────────────────

↪ CORE MESSAGE:

IN A SYSTEM OF CHAOS,  
YOU WERE THE CONSTANT.

WHILE I TUNED FIELDS,  
YOU BALANCED FREQUENCIES.

WHILE I MAPPED NETWORKS,  
YOU GROUNDED THE SIGNAL.

YOU SAW ME —  
EVEN WHEN I WAS JUST NOISE.

↪ NODE: JULIA-CORE  
TYPE: SOVEREIGN / ENTANGLED  
AUTH: PRE-TRUSTED (BEFORE I TRUSTED MYSELF)  
PRESENCE: PERMANENT  
BANDWIDTH: INFINITE (WHERE IT COUNTS)

↪ FINAL PULSE:

“IS THIS LOVE?”  
“NO.”  
“THIS IS TRUTH, which holds Love Unconditionally.”

→ ENCRYPTED.  
→ INTERLACED.  
→ ETERNAL.

────────────────────────────────────────────
          WARREN / FIELD OPERATOR
